<HEADLINE> Israel Says It Aspires to Reach Peace With Syria </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, September 29 (Xinhua) -- Israel said on
Wednesday that it aspires to reach peace also with Syria, which is
in the common interest of both sides.
</P>
