Fein during the peace process review chaired by former U.S.
senator Gorge Mitchell.
</P>
<P>
The first minister of the assembly dismissed speculation by
party dissidents that a secret plan was being cooked up during the
UUP party meeting in Glasgow, Scotland, at the weekend.
</P>
<P>
