<TEXT>
<P>
LUANDA, September 29 (Xinhua) -- Angola will continue to insist
on the one-China policy, recognizing the People's Republic of
China as its sole legitimate government, Acting Foreign Minister
Toco Serao said here Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Serao made the statement at a meeting with Chinese Ambassador
to Angola Jiang Yuande, adding that " despite of any actions" of
the Taiwan authorities, Angola will constantly insist on the
one-China policy.
</P>
