states" theory thrown out by Lee Teng-hui.
</P>
<P>
Angola has been attaching great importance to the Sino-Angolan
relations, Serao said, stressing that the development of the
bilateral relations enjoys privileges in Angola's foreign policy.
</P>
<P>
Angolan Foreign Minister Joao Miranda is currently in New York
for participating in the General Assembly of the United Nations.
