<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, September 30 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 6,071.12 points on Thursday,
down 25.54 points, or 0.42 percent, from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was active with the turnover reaching over 82
trillion Turkish Liras (over 178 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index dropped 31.29 points, or 0.40 percent,
to close at 7,755.94 points, the services index fell 78.44
points, or 1.11 percent, to close at 6,622,36 points while the
industrial index rose 1.00 point, or 0.01 percent, to close at
4,513.72 points. 
</P>
