<HEADLINE> People's Daily Hails PRC's 50th Founding Anniversary (4) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It continues to say that facts have proved that the Chinese
people could possess immense power by uniting as one and striving
together as long as they receive correct guidance, master
scientific theories, establish an advanced social system and map
out correct policies and principles.
</P>
<P>
Glorifying the achievements the Chinese people have made in
building a new China and in socialist construction, the editorial
hails the people as the sole driving force for making history.
</P>
<P>
It also pays tribute to the first and second generations of
China's central collective leadership with Mao Zedong and Deng
Xiaoping at the core, respectively, saying their historic
contributions and achievements could not be forgotten at this
momentous and festive moment of the 50th anniversary of new China.
</P>
<P>
Hailing the central collective leadership with Comrade Jiang
Zemin at the core as a mature one with lofty ideals, firm
determination, and outstanding leadership abilities, the editorial
expresses full confidence in its leading the Chinese people to
create an epoch in the building of socialism with Chinese
characteristics.
</P>
<P>
The 15th Party Congress has mapped out the trans-century
blueprint: by the year 2010, the gross domestic product will be
double the figure of 2000, people's standard of living will become
better-off, and a basically complete socialist market system will
be established; by the year 2020, the national economy will become
even more developed and the various systems will be improved
further; and by the 100th anniversary of the founding of new China,
China will basically achieve modernization and develop into a
prosperous, democratic and civilized socialist country, according
to the editorial.
</P>
<P>
We should hold higher the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory,
unite closely around the Party's Central Committee with Comrade
Jiang Zemin at the core, unite as one, make continuous headway,
strive to advance the cause of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics into the 21st century, and press ahead to realize
the glorious rejuvenation of the Chinese nation, it says. 
