<HEADLINE> People's Daily Hails PRC's 50th Founding Anniversary (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The country's striving during the past five decades tells us
that only socialism could save China and develop the nation,
stresses the editorial.
</P>
<P>
The socialist system is an utterly new social system which is
designed for the people and relies on the people to emancipate and
develop the social productive forces and build a prosperous,
civilized, and democratic society free of oppression and
exploitation, the editorial says.
