<P>
"Facts have proved that this historical choice, which
determined the destiny of the Chinese people, has brought new life,
glorious achievements and a promising future for the nation," it
continues.
</P>
<P>
Pointing out that it is a tough and long process to build
socialism in an economically and culturally underdeveloped country
like China, the editorial notes that the knowledge about socialism
is deepening under the guidance of Marxism, Leninism, Mao Zedong
Thought and Deng Xiaoping Theory.
</P>
<P>
"Guided by Deng Xiaoping Theory, we have achieved enormous
success during the two decades since reform and opening-up," says
the editorial.
</P>
<P>
"The 50-year application of socialism in China indicates that
socialism as an utterly new social system develops in its practice
and changes to the needs of the time," it says. "The cause of
building socialism with Chinese characteristics will be forever
full of vitality and vigor if we unwaveringly adhere to the
principle of combining theory with practice, learning from the
masses, and persisting in development and innovation."
</P>
<P>
The glorious 50 years also illustrate that the Chinese people
are a great people who are hardworking, brave, unyielding, and
creative, it emphasizes.
</P>
<P>
"It's the people who turn the correct decisions of the Chinese
Communist Party and the advantages of socialism into reality," it
says.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
