<HEADLINE> Chinese, Russian Presidents Confer By Phone (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jiang went on to say that great changes have taken place in
China since the founding of the People's Republic of China,
especially since China adopted the reform and opening-up policy 20
years ago, and China is becoming increasingly prosperous.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese president noted that Sino-Russian relations are
developing smoothly and agreeably, and the two sides will continue
their efforts to constantly reinforce and enrich their bilateral
strategic cooperative partnership, Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
Jiang told Yeltsin that he is looking forward to the Russian
president's visit to China in November.  
</P>
</TEXT>
