<HEADLINE> Food Security Key to Progress: Kenyan President </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, September 30 (Xinhua) -- Kenyan President Daniel arap
Moi has stressed that self-sufficiency in food is crucial to
Kenya's economic success.
