to stage a repeat of the Australian Open semifinal against Thomas
Enqvist. Lapentti fought hard to record a three-set win over
Fernando Meligeni of Brazil, 6-4, 2-6, (7-6)16-14.
</P>
<P>
The Grand Slam Cup will not affect world rankings as it does
not carry points. 
